---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Fabrizio Guccione" description="Embedded Intelligence Designer at NYU ITP. ML + physical computing + fabrication.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <p data-reveal class="label mb-3">about</p>
    <h1 data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1" class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent-soft tracking-tight mb-10">
      the code is not the experience
    </h1>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-text-DEFAULT text-base leading-relaxed">
      <p data-reveal>
        I'm Fabrizio — an <strong class="text-accent-soft font-semibold">Embedded Intelligence Designer</strong>
        finishing my MPS at <a href="https://itp.nyu.edu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-underline">NYU ITP</a>.
        I build AI-driven interactive systems that live in physical space, not just on screens.
      </p>

      <p data-reveal>
        My grandmother in Italy taught me to sew. That's where I learned that the pattern is not the garment —
        the moment material meets the physical world, everything shifts. I think about this constantly when I build installations.
        The interesting part is always the thing you didn't design.
      </p>

      <p data-reveal>
        Currently I run ITP's Fabrication Shop, where I train 300+ students on laser cutting, CNC milling, 3D printing,
        and machine embroidery. I'm the person who translates between the code and the shop floor.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div data-reveal class="card mt-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-2">AI / ML</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Stable Diffusion, CLIP, Whisper, LLM APIs, Claude/GPT, MediaPipe, OpenCV, pose detection</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-2">Hardware</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Arduino, ESP32, OAK-D cameras, thermal printers, Raspberry Pi</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-2">Creative Coding</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">TouchDesigner, THREE.js, p5.js, Processing, GLSL</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-2">Fabrication</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Laser cutting, CNC, 3D printing, machine embroidery, pattern making, sewing</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div data-reveal class="mt-12">
      <p class="label mb-4">experience</p>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-DEFAULT font-medium">Fabrication Shop Staff</p>
            <p class="text-text-dim">NYU ITP</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-dim font-mono text-xs">2025–now</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-DEFAULT font-medium">Graduate Assistant</p>
            <p class="text-text-dim">NYU ITP</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-dim font-mono text-xs">2025</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-DEFAULT font-medium">ITP Camp Counselor</p>
            <p class="text-text-dim">NYU ITP</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-dim font-mono text-xs">2025</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-DEFAULT font-medium">Creative Technology</p>
            <p class="text-text-dim">McCann New York</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-dim font-mono text-xs">2024</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-DEFAULT font-medium">Junior Web Designer</p>
            <p class="text-text-dim">NYU CREATE Lab</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-dim font-mono text-xs">2023</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-DEFAULT font-medium">Fashion Design Intern</p>
            <p class="text-text-dim">ADEAM New York</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-dim font-mono text-xs">2022</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div data-reveal class="mt-12 flex gap-5 flex-wrap text-sm">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/fabriziog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-underline">linkedin</a>
      <a href="https://x.com/fabricated_it" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-underline">x</a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/fabricated.it/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-underline">instagram</a>
      <a href="https://guccione.work" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-underline">portfolio</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/FabriGu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-underline">github</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
